Today, I'll show you how to create a tool that automatically scans a specified folder for Excel files and generates a detailed inventory list with comprehensive file information.

### ğŸ¯ What This Tool Does

- âœ… Automatically scans folders for all Excel files
- âœ… Lists filenames, sizes, and modification dates
- âœ… Saves results as a new Excel file
- âœ… Auto-generates summary information
- âœ… Just run it! No manual work required

